      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/30/1/1/38",
      "text": [
        " أخذَ الله ميثاقَ المؤمن ِعلى ألاّ يُصَدّقَ في مقالته ولا يُنتَصَفَ من عَدوّه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.muhajir-b-ali": [
          "38. It has been narrated that Abu 'Abd Allah (a.s) said: Allah has taken a pledge from the believer that his words will be belied and that he would not be able to avenge himself against his enemy."
        ]
      }
    },
